  <li class="bold">General Information</li>
    <p class="li-para">Helen Bernhard Bakery respects the privacy of our customers, business partners, employees and job applicants and other visitors to our websites who may choose to provide personal information. We recognize the need for appropriate protections and management of personal information that you provide to us. This Privacy Statement will assist you in understanding what types of information we may collect, how that information may be used, and with whom the information may be shared.</p>

  <li class="bold">When Ordering</li>
    <p class="li-para">All custom decorated orders are to be paid in full when the order is placed either by phone or in person at the bakery. All online orders for In-Store pickup are paid in advance in full online when order is placed on www.helenbernhardbakery.com.</p>

  <li class="bold">Refund/Exchange Policy</li>
    <p class="li-para">We take pride in our desserts and cakes. If you are unhappy with your order and/or purchase, immediately notify us (within 24 hours of pick-up) of your concern and return your dessert to us. We will give you credit for the amount returned for use toward a future purchase. All refunds will be provided as a credit to the credit card used or an in-store credit, i.e. Helen Bernhard Bakery Gift Card within five (5) business days upon receipt of the returned merchandise.  You must bring receipt of purchase with you.</p>

  <li class="bold">Order Cancellation Policy</li>
    <p class="li-para">Helen Bernhard Bakery understands that plans change and we will gladly assist you in making changes to your order date and time whenever possible. We accept weekday cancellations by phone or email (helenbernhard@aol.com) prior to 2:00 pm, 2 business days before your event. All changes must be handled directly with a representative of Helen Bernhard Bakery and confirmed. Helen Bernhard Bakery reserves the right to charge a cancellation fee if insufficient time is given, as stated above, due to costs incurred in the purchase, priority and preparation of the order. Charges for cancellations after the above time will be as follows: 25% of the entire order will be charged for cancellations 24 hours prior to the event and 100% of the entire order will be charged for canceling the order after that time. It is entirely up to Helen Bernhard Bakery discretion, to change or otherwise offer any other options to the customer. Special orders (Highly Decorated Cakes) that are not picked up will NOT be refunded. Orders that require delivery and cannot be delivered due to customer’s wrong information or availability will be taken back to Helen Bernhard Bakery and stored until further notice from customer. Should you require a future delivery date, you will be held responsible for an additional delivery charge. Because of the nature of our business and our quality and freshness assurance, we will dispose of any cake, cupcake, baked item that is not picked up or delivered within 48 hours after the due time and you will NOT be refunded due to the above rules. To see the bakeries “Holiday Hours” please refer to the Holiday Calendar.</p>

  <li class="bold">Wedding & Grooms Cake Cancellation Policy</li>
    <p class="li-para">Wedding deposits are non-refundable & non-transferable (Deposit is deducted from the wedding cake balance only). Any Wedding or Groom’s cake orders cancelled 2 weeks prior to your wedding date will receive only a 75% refund on any payments made after the deposit. Any Wedding or Groom’s cake orders cancelled less than 1 week prior to your wedding date will receive a  no refunds on any payments made after the deposit.</p>

  <li class="bold">Change Order</li>
    <p class="li-para">There will be a $15 Change Order fee for any changes that are requested within 24 hours of the time required.</p>

  <li class="bold">Highly Decorated Cake Orders</li>
    <p class="li-para">Highly decorated cakes include wedding cakes, grooms cakes, sculpted cakes and cut-out cakes. The latest time available to order a Highly Decorated cake is the Wednesday prior to the weekend required at noon. The above Order Cancellation Policy will apply for those situations. During peak holiday season Helen Bernhard Bakery reserves the right to adjust the cut-off date if orders have exceeded our production capabilities.</p>

  <li class="bold">Decorations and Coloring</li>
    <p class="li-para">We have highly skilled decorators.  We will do our best to match any requested color or design.  We are limited to the fact that we are dealing with icing that can fade do to light and temperature so we do not garauntee an exact match.  Also do to the nature of drawings, we will make our best representation of what is requested but are again limited by the nature of our product.</p>

  <li class="bold">Image editing</li>

    <p class="li-para">We do not offer touch up or color adjustments.  Minor cropping may occur in order to fit image to cake/space available.</p>

  <li class="bold">Copyright</li>

    <p class="li-para">Copyright images will not be printed.  In order for copyright images to be reproduced, authoritative letters from governing body to whom the image has been copyrighted to will be requested and needed upon placement of order.</p>

