  <li class="bold">1/2 Price Sunday Product</li>

    <p class="li-para">Any product purchased on Sunday at 1/2 price is sold as is.  It cannot be returned or refunded.  This product has been stored for an extended period of time and we will not guarantee freshness or moisture of the cake and icing.  There also may be some damage to decoration.
    We sell product at 1/2 price on a first come, first serve basis.  Call ahead for 1/2 price merchandise is not allowed.</p>

  <li class="bold">Shipping Policy</li>

    <p class="li-para">Helen Bernhard Bakery takes great pride in Products. Please be advised that UPS DOES NOT deliver to APO/FPO or other Military addresses. The person you are shipping to can expect their Product to arrive by 3:00pm or 4:30pm the next business day to commercial destinations if requested to ship UPS Red. End of day to residential locations. Friday Shippers for a Saturday delivery require an additional $15 charge added at checkout! Place Orders to multiple locations separately. PLEASE INFORM THE RECIPIENT TO EXPECT SHIPMENT! Delays resulting from inclement weather are not covered. Once a delivery has been attempted (a call tag left) delays resulting from setting up a second delivery attempt or pick-up are not covered. We offer two options for delays resulting from the shipper. Please be mindful that if the bakery runs into issues baking your product in time for UPS delivery we may have to ship on the next available ship day.<br>
    <br>
    1) Refund shipping charges if you wish to keep the Product or<br>
    <br>
    2) Product reshipped if you wish to return the delayed cake but not necessary due to possible spoilage.<br>
    <br>
    If the product is damaged in shipping, we will gladly process a damage claim with UPS. Claims must be made within 5 days of receipt. The shipping company may require that the damaged product, box & all items included in package be picked up for inspection; so please do not discard the box, product or any of its contents. Damage & unsuccessful deliveries are not common – ONLY 1 – 1.5 % claims are processed per season from all of the cakes that we ship. No refunds are given for incomplete or wrong addresses. Packages left at the door – sometimes a shipper will leave the package at the door if they determine it is safe. Apartments, Condos, Dormitories, Hotels, Hospitals – shipments are usually directed to a complex office or receiving department which may result in delays. We recommend letting the recipient know they will be receiving a package so they can be on the look-out for it. No refunds are given due to this delay. No deliveries are accepted at Military Bases or P.O. Boxes. Deliveries to extended delivery areas are not guaranteed. International deliveries are not recommended because of the distance of travel for a perishable item. Products are perishable food items and therefore cannot be returned. Credit card authorization and verification must be received prior to processing an order. UPS shipments occur Tuesday through Friday, excluding holidays for Next Day Air delivery unless otherwise noted i.e, Ground Shipment. Additional questions or problems may be directed to our shipping department and will be handled on individual basis according to our store policy.<br>
    <br>
    PLEASE NOTE: Out of state orders WILL NOT be charged sales tax.</p>

